<%
title "Features"
description "Sheethub Features"
keywords %w(features benefits)
%>

<div class="white-container">
<div id="features" class="container">
    <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h1>SheetHub for Musicians</h1>
        <h2>You upload your amazing work - we take care of everything else.</h2>


        <div id="carousel-features" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <!-- Indicators -->
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carousel-features" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-features" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-features" data-slide-to="2"></li>
          </ol>

          <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
          <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
            <div class="item active">
              <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/sheethub/assets/screenshot1.png">
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/sheethub/assets/screenshot4.png">
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/sheethub/assets/screenshot3.png">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br/>

        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Easy Publishing</h3>
                    <p>Compose, publish, sell. Easily publish, manage, and update your music to a growing audience of musicians. Add files, video links, set a price, and more. No complex installation or technical skills required.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-users"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Direct-to-fan storefront</h3>
                    <p>Sell your work directly to your fans with a product page. You can start publishing on SheetHub, your website, Facebook page, or Twitter channel in minutes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-smile-o"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Zero Upfront Fees</h3>
                    <p>SheetHub costs nothing up-front to use. You are free to upload an unlimited number of commercial works. No setup fees, no monthly fees, no hosting fees to worry about!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-money"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Pay Only When You Sell</h3>
                    <p>We are your true partners and your success is our success! That's why we offer one of the most generous payouts. You keep <strong>85%</strong> (90% for Pro)!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-bank"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Get Paid Instantly</h3>
                    <p>Who likes waiting for their own money? No one. Get paid instantly and directly to your PayPal account the moment a user completes a purchase. </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-credit-card"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Say Yes To Every Customer</h3>
                    <p>Accept major credit cards from customers all over the world, including Visa, MasterCard, American Express, and Discover.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-legal"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>EU VAT Compliance <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>SheetHub makes it possible to be VAT MOSS compliant in 2015 by providing publishers with all the information they need to file your taxes to the VAT MOSS system.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-line-chart"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Analytics</h3>
                    <p>Gain valuable insight into your overall earnings, your most popular works, who your fans are, and more from an intuitive and simple to use dashboard that’s, well, kind of fun to use.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-truck"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Secure Storage and Delivery</h3>
                    <p>Files are saved over a secure link and only released to your customer via a timed or download limited link. This stops people passing on the download link to other people who aren’t planning on paying.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-search"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>SEO Optimized</h3>
                    <p>Clean, search engine friendly code and proper tagging to help you get found by people looking for your work.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-certificate"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>PDF Stamping <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>Discourage the illegal sharing of your PDF products by stamping them with the name and email of your customer. With their ‘fingerprint’ on it, people are less likely to sell or share your content.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-shopping-cart"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Pay-What-You-Want Pricing <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>You always get to set the minimum price for your music, but that doesn’t stop your fans from giving more in the spirit of supporting you! Let your biggest fans decide how much they pay you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-link"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Your Own Personal Website <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>Signing up gives you your own personal website at username.sheethub.co that showcases all the works you've published on SheetHub.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-tree"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Getting Better Every Day</h3>
                    <p>SheetHub is a continuously evolving platform built to cater the needs of our growing community of musicians. The community decides and votes on what we build next. You shape the future of SheetHub!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-lightbulb-o"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>We're here to help</h3>
                    <p>We're musicians too, and we're here to help. Whether you have questions, need help setting up, or just need some advice. <%= link_to "We're available anytime.", support_url %></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>

    <% if !user_signed_in? %>
        <a href="<%= new_user_registration_url %>" class="btn btn-lg btn-success center-block"> Sign Up</a>
    <% end %>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <h1>SheetHub for Fans</h1>
        <h2>Discover new music by tags and recommendations. Favorite, share, and keep your purchases forever.</h2>

        <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/sheethub/assets/screenshot2.png" />

        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-tags"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Tags</h3>
                    <p>Filter by genres, composers, instruments, and sources to easily find works you care about.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-birthday-cake"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>DRM-Free</h3>
                    <p>No Flash, no proprietary software to install, no restrictive copy protection. Buy once, keep forever.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-gift"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Access to Free works</h3>
                    <p>Get unlimited downloads of free published works on SheetHub. Download and print anytime, on any platform.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-credit-card"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Multiple Payment Options</h3>
                    <p>Pay with PayPal, or with major credit cards including Visa, MasterCard, American Express, and Discover.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-share-alt"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Socially Engaging</h3>
                    <p>Share new and interesting pieces with your fellow musicians on major social networks.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-6">
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-heart-o"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Recommendations <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>Easily discover new and interesting music through recommended tags and pieces.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-download"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Re-download past purchases</h3>
                    <p>Permanent access to the high-quality download of all your purchases.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-hand-o-up"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Instant Buy</h3>
                    <p>Instant buy makes purchasing as simple and easy as possible. Just click, pay and download your product.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-bookmark-o"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Favorites <span class="badge pro">NEW</span></h3>
                    <p>Bookmark your most favorite works for later perusal and purchase.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <div class="col-xs-1">
                    <em class="fa fa-comments-o"></em>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-11">
                    <h3>Discussions</h3>
                    <p>Give constructive feedback to the author, post your performance recordings, and discuss the piece with others.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    <% if !user_signed_in? %>
        <a href="<%= new_user_registration_url %>" class="btn btn-lg btn-success center-block"> Sign Up</a>
    <% end %>
</div>
</div>

<% if !user_signed_in? %>
<div class="animated-banner footer-banner">
    <h1>Join a growing community of musicians. <a href="<%= new_user_registration_url %>" class="btn btn-inline btn-success btn-banner btn-lg center-block"><em class="fa fa-user"></em> Sign Up For Free</a></h1>
</div>
<% end %>

<% if user_signed_in? %>
<div class="animated-banner footer-banner">
    <h1>Now available: Plus and Pro memberships. <a href="<%= upgrade_url %>" class="btn btn-success btn-inline btn-banner btn-lg center-block"><em class="fa fa-star"></em> Go Pro</a></h1>
</div>
<% end %>